com.interpss.core.aclf.contingency

Interface MultiOutageContingency

  • All Superinterfaces:
    BaseContingency, com.hazelcast.nio.serialization.DataSerializable, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, NameTag, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    BusbarOutageContingency, Xfr3WOutageContingency
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    BusbarOutageContingencyImpl, MultiOutageContingencyImpl, Xfr3WOutageContingencyImpl

    public interface MultiOutageContingency
extends BaseContingency
    A representation of the model object 'Multi Outage Contingency'. A class for modeling a multi-outage contingency

    The following features are supported:

    • Outage Type
    • Outage Branches
    See Also:
    ContingencyPackage.getMultiOutageContingency()
